  _textsByLanguages:
  - _languageType: 0
    _text: "\u0412\u044B \u043F\u043E\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0438\u0442\u0435 100 \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0435\u0442,
      \u043F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0435 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u043C\u043E\u0442\u0440\u0430
      \u0440\u0435\u043A\u043B\u0430\u043C\u044B"
  - _languageType: 1
    _text: You'll receive 100 coins after watching the ad
  - _languageType: 2
    _text: "Reklam\u0131 izledikten sonra 100 jeton kazanacaks\u0131n\u0131z"
  - _languageType: 3
    _text: "Recibir\xE1s 100 monedas tras ver el anuncio"
  - _languageType: 4
    _text: "Sie erhalten 100 M\xFCnzen, nachdem Sie sich die Werbung angesehen haben"
  - _languageType: 5
    _text: "Vous recevrez 100 pi\xE8ces apr\xE8s avoir visionn\xE9 la publicit\xE9"
